quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,79,( Yousuf ne ) kaha ke khuda panah mein rakhay ke jis shakhs ke paas hum ne apni cheez payi hai is ke siwa kisi aur ko pakar len aisa karen to hum ( barray ) be insaaf hain
12,80,jab woh is se na umeed hogaye to allag ho kar Salah karne lagey. sab se barray ne kahakiya tum nahi jantay ke tumahray waalid ne tum se khuda ka ehad liya hai aur is se pehlay bhi tum Yousuf ke baray mein qasoor kar chuke ho to jab taq waalid sahib mujhe hukum nah den mein to is jagah se hilnay ka nahi ya khuda mere liye koi aur tadbeer kere. aur woh sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai
12,81,tum sab waalid sahib ke paas wapas jao aur kaho ke abba aap ke sahibzaday ne ( wahan ja kar ) chori ki. aur hum ne apni Danist ke mutabiq aap se ( is ke le anay ka ) ehadkiya tha magar hum ghaib ki baton ko jan-nay aur yaad rakhnay walay to nahi they
12,82,aur jis bastii mein hum ( thehray ) they wahan se ( yani ahal misar se ) aur jis qaafley mein aeye hain is se daryaft kar lijiye aur hum is bayan mein bilkul sachey hain
12,83,( jab unhon ne yeh baat Yaqoob se aa kar kahi to ) unhon ne kaha ke ( haqeeqat yun nahi hai ) balkay yeh baat tum ne apne dil se banali hai to sabr hi behtar hai. ajab nahi ke khuda un sab ko mere paas le aeye. be shak woh Dana ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
12,84,phir un ke paas se chalay gay aur kehnay lagey haae afsos Yousuf ( haae afsos ) aur ranj ЩҲШ§Щ„Щ… mein ( is qader roye ke ) un ki ankhen safaid hogyin aur un ka dil gham se bhar raha tha
12,85,betay kehnay lagey ke п»ӯпәҚп»ҹп» п»Ә agar aap Yousuf ko isi terhan yaad hi karte rahen ge to ya to bemaar ho jaien ge ya jaan hi day den ge
12,86,unhon ne kaha ke mein apne gham ЩҲШ§ЩҶШҜЩҲЫҒ ka izhaar khuda se karta hon. aur khuda ki taraf se woh baatein jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay
